{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji19","name":"毛泽东全集第19卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji19.pdf"],"article":{"title":"复河南区党委电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"复河南区党委电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1945年3月1日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华北各根据地因长期战争，连年旱灾，财政均感困难，你们必须确定与坚持自力更生的财政原则，不要希望外援。但中央仍决定由华北各根据地共帮助你们伪联币一千万元作资本，嗣后即须全部自给。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1].这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的复河南区党委电的主要内容。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1945,"month":3,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":344,"page_end":344},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}